  - Title: Qur’ân
    Location: XXXIX 29
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=‘Duo Sunt in Homine’
  - Combat-Action=Holy War
---
Allâh coineth a similitude： A man in relation to whom are several
part-owners, quarrelling, and a man belonging wholly to one man. Are
the two equal in similitude?  Praise be to Allâh! But most of them
know not.
